---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mikey Somatics | Trauma-Informed Somatic Healing & Wellness">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center py-20">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-4">Mikey Alexander, ITP</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light leading-tight text-forest mb-6">
          Somatic Therapy for Stress, Anxiety, and Trauma Recovery
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Guided body-based sessions to process unresolved stress, calm your nervous system, and foster emotional balance.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-forest text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-forest-light transition-colors">
          Book Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <img src="/images/hero-aura.png" alt="Somatic healing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Points -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold">Accepting new clients</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold">60-minute appointments</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold">Telehealth available anywhere in the US</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold">Trauma healing for depression, anxiety & dissociative symptoms</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Approach -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/nature-polaroid.png" alt="Nature and healing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">My Approach</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-6">Keeping it Simple.</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          In a world full of complexity, I believe the best path forward is simple&mdash;though not always easy. My focus is on helping you reconnect with your body as a source of wisdom and healing. I create a safe, supportive space to explore how your body holds onto experiences and emotions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Using somatic healing, internal family systems, and pain reprocessing therapy, we'll work together to release tension, process past stress, and build a sense of safety within yourself. My approach is practical, compassionate, and grounded in helping you find balance, resilience, and well-being.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="text-forest font-medium hover:text-forest-light transition-colors underline underline-offset-4">
          Learn more &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modalities -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Modalities</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest">How We Work Together</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/images/modality-icon-1.png" alt="Somatic Experiencing" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 object-contain" />
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Somatic Experiencing</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/images/modality-3.png" alt="Pain Reprocessing" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 object-contain" />
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Pain Reprocessing</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/images/modality-4.png" alt="Breathwork" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 object-contain" />
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Breathwork</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/images/modality-icon-2.png" alt="Parts Work" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 object-contain" />
        <h3 class="text-forest font-semibold mb-2">Parts Work (IFS)</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trauma Informed Care -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Trauma Informed Care</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-forest mb-6">A Safe Space for Your Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          In trauma-informed care, my role is to be a compassionate guide as you navigate your healing journey. Together, we create a safe, affirming container where you can explore your experiences at your own pace.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          I honor your unique history and identity, recognizing the profound impact trauma has on the mind, body, spirit, and relationships. This approach fosters empowerment, connection, and healing across all aspects of your being, helping you reconnect with yourself, build resilience, and find balance and control in your life.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/peaceful-room.png" alt="Peaceful room for somatic healing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Remote Care -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-forest text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-widest uppercase text-sage mb-3">Remote Care</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light mb-6">Sessions From Anywhere</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I conduct sessions virtually and find that many times clients enjoy the familiarity and safety of their homes. I also recognize that this isn't always the case and a feasible option for everyone.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        I am happy to work on a solution to meeting in person, in the Hudson Valley Area, that feels safe and private for you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-forest px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-sand transition-colors font-medium">
        Book Free Consult
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
